                  <span class="bg-white text-gray-800 font-semibold px-4 md:px-6 py-2 md:py-3 text-sm md:text-base rounded-full shadow-md transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105 cursor-pointer">
                    Learn More
                  </span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base mt-4 md:mt-6 px-2">
                  Use Case: A one-stop platform for job searching and AI-based interviews.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </a>

          <div class="mt-4 md:mt-6">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start gap-3 md:gap-4">
              <div class="flex-1">
